data.description: Welcome to your dream home on the Southside of Corpus Christi. This beautifully maintained residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience, making it a must-see for anyone seeking a slice of paradise in this vibrant community. Only 3 years old, this home offers an amazing open floorplan perfect for entertaining. The secondary bedrooms offer built in drawers and ample closet space. The master bedroom suite is oversized to provide a sitting area that walks into your grand master bath with double vanities, jetted tub, tiled shower and closet. And let's not forget your back yard. A covered patio for outdoor dining, great yard space to create your backyard escape and no back neighbors! Come, see and make this home yours today!!
